author: Sarah Whitten
title: Walmart to offer rent relief to shops within its stores and ease financing for suppliers
description: Walmart is offering some help to its small business partners as the coronavirus pandemic forces consumers to self-isolate and companies to shutter their storefronts.
content:
Walmart said Wednesday it is offering help to its small business partners as the coronavirus forces consumers to self-isolate and companies to shut stores.
